						<h4>Jane Ciabattari</h4>
												<p>Jane Ciabattari, author of the short story collection <em>Stealing the Fire,</em> is a former National Book Critics Circle president (currently on the Advisory Board ) and a member of the Writers Grotto and Page Street. Her reviews, interviews and cultural criticism have appeared in NPR, BBC Culture, the <em>New York Times Book Review, the Guardian, Bookforum, Paris Review, the Washington Post, Boston Globe,</em> and the <em>Los Angeles Times</em>, among other publications.</p>
